TEST FIXTURE DO NOT DELETE: Introducing GymX for mobile

subject: TEST FIXTURE DO NOT DELETE: Introducing GymX for mobile
html:
Dear Mr. Strong,

I hope this email finds you well. I'm writingclear to introduce you to GymX, a mobile app designed to help gym-goers track their workouts, set goals, and stay motivated.

A key feature of GymX is we use machine learning to identify all the workout moves.

If you're interested in learning more, I would be happy to provide you with a demo of the app and answer any questions you may have. Please let me know if this is something you'd be interested in.

Thank you for your time,
John Smith
